name: Google Aero! - Icon Pack
css:
@namespace url("http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml");

@-moz-document url-prefix("http://www.google"),              url-prefix("https://www.google"),
               url-prefix("http://images.google"),           url-prefix("https://images.google"),
               url-prefix("http://maps.google"),             url-prefix("https://maps.google"),
               url-prefix("http://news.google"),             url-prefix("https://news.google"),
               url-prefix("http://groups.google"),           url-prefix("https://groups.google"),
               url-prefix("http://books.google"),            url-prefix("https://books.google"),
               url-prefix("http://scholar.google"),          url-prefix("https://scholar.google"),
               url-prefix("http://mail.google"),             url-prefix("https://mail.google"),
               url-prefix("http://blogsearch.google"),       url-prefix("https://blogsearch.google"),
               url-prefix("http://translate.google"),        url-prefix("https://translate.google"),
               url-prefix("http://www.google.com/calendar"), url-prefix("https://www.google.com/calendar"),
               url-prefix("http://picasaweb.google"),        url-prefix("https://picasaweb.google"),
               url-prefix("http://video.google"),            url-prefix("https://video.google"),
               url-prefix("http://docs.google"),             url-prefix("https://docs.google"),
               url-prefix("http://sites.google"),            url-prefix("https://sites.google"),
               url-prefix("http://finance.google"),          url-prefix("https://finance.google") {

a:before {
  display: inline-block !important;
  width: 16px !important;
  height: 16px !important;
  vertical-align: top !important;
  margin-right: 2px !important;
  background-image: url("data:image/png;base64,") !important;
}

a[href*=".google."][href*="/accounts/Login"]:before,
a[href*=".google."][href*="/accounts/ClearSID"]:before,
a[href*=".google."][href*="/groups/signout"]:before,
a[href*=".google."][href*="/Logout"]:before,
a[href*=".google."][href*="/logout"]:before,
a[href*=".google."][href*="?logout"]:before                 { background-position:  -16px 0px !important; content: "" !important; } /* Logout */
a[href*=".google."][href*="/history/"]:before               { background-position:  -32px 0px !important; content: "" !important; } /* History */
a[href^="/maps/user?"],
a[href*=".google."][href*="/accounts/ManageAccount"]:before { background-position:   -0px 0px !important; content: "" !important; } /* My Profile, Account Settings */
a[href*=".google."][href*="/support"]:before                { background-position:  -64px 0px !important; content: "" !important; } /* Help */
a[href*="/advanced_search?"]:before                         { background-position:  -48px 0px !important; content: "" !important; } /* Advanced Search */
a[href*=".google."][href*="#settings"]:before,
a[href*="/preferences?"]:before                             { background-position:  -80px 0px !important; content: "" !important; } /* Search Settings */ 
a[href*="/shoppinglist?"]:before                            { background-position:  -96px 0px !important; content: "" !important; } /* My Shopping List */
a[href*=".google."][href*="pref=ig"]:before                 { background-position: -112px 0px !important; content: "" !important; } /* iGoogle */

}
